                <div class="bag">
                    <h1 class="secBoxl"><span>P&aacute;gina no encontrada</span></h1>
                    <h2>La p&aacute;gina solicitada no est&aacute; disponible por haber cambiado la direcci&oacute;n (URL) o no existir. Disculpe las molestias.</h2>
                    <p>Con frecuencia es debido a alg&uacute;n error al escribir la direcci&oacute;n de la p&aacute;gina (URL). Compru&eacute;belo de nuevo y aseg&uacute;rese de que escribe la direcci&oacute;n correctamente.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><span aria-hidden="true">&#8226;&#8226;&#8226;</span> Volver a la <a href="_volver" onclick="history.back(); return false;" onkeypress="history.back(); return false" title="Volver a la p&aacute;gina anterior">p&aacute;gina anterior</a>.</li>
                        <li><span aria-hidden="true">&#8226;&#8226;&#8226;</span> Ir a la <a title="Ir a www.rtve.es" href="https://www.rtve.es/">p&aacute;gina de inicio</a> de RTVE.es</li>
                        <li><span aria-hidden="true">&#8226;&#8226;&#8226;</span> Ir a <a title="Ir a www.rtve.es/play" href="https://www.rtve.es/play/">RTVE Play</a>.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <span class="ghost">Versi&oacute;n en ingl&eacute;s del texto</span>
                <div class="bag english" lang="en">
                    <h2>Sorry, but the page you're trying to view is not available, either because its URL has changed or it doesn't exist anymore.</h2>
                    <p>Frequently, this is due to spelling errors when writing the page URL. Please, check your spelling and try again</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><span aria-hidden="true">&#8226;&#8226;&#8226;</span> Go back to the <a href="_volver" onclick="history.back(); return false;" onkeypress="history.back(); return false" title="Go back to the previous page">previous page</a>.</li>
                        <li><span aria-hidden="true">&#8226;&#8226;&#8226;</span> Go to RTVE.es <a title="Go to www.rtve.es" href="https://www.rtve.es/">main page</a>.</li>
                        <li><span aria-hidden="true">&#8226;&#8226;&#8226;</span> Go to <a title="Go to www.rtve.es/play" href="https://www.rtve.es/play/">RTVE Play</a>.</li>
